      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and is ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches upon close inspection, consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has been serviced regularly, making it a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid, honest car without the premium price of a mint-condition model.",
