      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously curated vehicle, offered in truly impeccable condition. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, presenting in showroom-quality form both mechanically and aesthetically. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that defies its age and mirrors its original delivery state, this offering represents an unparalleled acquisition opportunity. All original appointments remain intact, reflecting a history of fastidious care.",
