    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s been kept in absolutely pristine shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! Always garaged, super clean, and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and pampered, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
