      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. The naturally aspirated power plant features individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering linear torque and an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen features the sought-after 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing precise damping adjustments. Meticulously maintained, the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical failure points\u2014have been addressed preventatively. The factory finish remains flawless, showing no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the interior retains original bolster integrity and tactile switchgear functionality.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No scratches or dents. Full service records included. Clean title.",
      "price": 44500.0,
