    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2020 Luxury Sport Sedan is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features original factory paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, entirely free of swirls, rock chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, retaining its original scent with zero signs of wear on the premium leather bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at an authorized dealership, and I possess a complete binder of all maintenance records. It has never seen rain, has never been through an automated car wash, and has been owned exclusively by a non-smoker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
